snippet.title: F1® 23 | Official Gameplay Features Deep Dive
snippet.description:
Check out the first F1® 23 Deep Dive, narrated by Sky Sports F1 presenter Natalie Pinkham. Get more information on F1® 23's updated vehicle physics and handling, the return of red flags, and the authentic recreations of the Las Vegas and Qatar grands prix.

Find out more about F1® 23: http://x.ea.com/f123/deepdive1 

F1® 23 arrives on June 16, 2023 for PlayStation 4|5, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, and PC.

Pre-order the F1® 23 Champions Edition now to get 3 days early access and exclusive content: http://x.ea.com/76543  

Subscribe to get the latest from the grid: http://x.ea.com/76558 

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/EASPORTSF1
